NG0505:330: mi mdza' rnams kyang med par 'gyur //

NG0505:332: nang gi rdzas kyang med par 'gyur //

NG0505:336: 'jig rten chos kyis ci la phan //

NG0505:353: rtog pa rags la chags sdang che //
NG0505:354: gsod la dga' zhing dmar la rngam //

NG0505:357: yod pas mi chog med la brnab //

NG0505:365: 'khor ba'i bde ba sdug bsngal yin //

NG0505:371: sdug bsngal rba la g.yeng tsam na //
NG0505:373: mi gtsang khrod kyi srin bu bzhin //
NG0505:374: bde ba la chags sdug bsngal grub //

NG0505:385: yi dwags zas mthong tshe na dgra //
NG0505:386: gshed pos gtse ba'i duhkha dang *//

NG0505:393: byang chub sems gcig ma gtogs pa //
NG0505:394: zad pa med par rgyun du 'khor //
NG0505:395: mu mtha' yod par ngas ma mthong *//

NG0505:408: srog las 'phangs pa'i blo bur nas //
NG0505:409: nyam nga med pa'i bsam pa yis //
NG0505:410: lus la lcags gzer stong btab cing *//

NG0505:976: yod pa'i lam du mi 'gro ba'i //

NG0505:1184: rang gzhan snga phyi bzang ngan can //
NG0505:1185: dman pa'i sems skyed nyan rang rgyu //
NG0505:1186: rgyal po sngon la chu sgrol bzhin //
NG0505:1187: rang nyid sngon la byang chub nas //
NG0505:1190: lug rdzi kun gyis mjug sdud bzhin //
NG0505:1191: sems can thams cad ma grol bar //
NG0505:1193: byang chub sems ni stobs med 'gyur //
NG0505:1194: de bas mtha' gnyis bral ba yi //
NG0505:1195: thams cad mkhyen pa'i smon lam gdab //
NG0505:1197: sems can kun la phan par 'gyur //
NG0505:1198: byang chub sems skyed nam mkha' bzhin //
NG0505:1199: rgyun chad med cing phyogs mtha' bral //
NG0505:1200: byang chub smon pa'i sems skyed de //
NG0505:1201: bu tsha'i dus kyi 'dun pa yang *//
NG0505:1202: mi chen gyur nas rdzogs pa bzhin //
NG0505:1203: 'dun pa'i rtsol ba cher yod de //
NG0505:1204: phal pa rnams kyis 'grub pa la //
NG0505:1205: byang chub sems dpa' smos ci dgos //
NG0505:1206: gang la zhugs pa'i sngon rol du //
NG0505:1207: byang chub sems ni rab bskyed cing *//
NG0505:1208: don de nyid la 'jug pa dang *//
NG0505:1209: rjes su sems kyis bsngos pa na //
NG0505:1210: stobs dang nus pa cher 'phel nas //
NG0505:1211: gang la zhugs pa'i don kun la //
NG0505:1212: mi nus mi shes mi 'grub pa //
NG0505:1213: med par byang chub sems kyis 'grub //
NG0505:1214: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'phrin las kun //
NG0505:1215: 'jug pa nyid du smin pas byung *//
NG0505:1216: byang chub sems la phyogs med pas //
NG0505:1217: sangs rgyas nyid la mtha' med do //
NG0505:1218: byang chub sems la dmigs med pas //
NG0505:1219: gdul bya nyid la rigs med do //
NG0505:1220: byang chub sems la dus med pas //
NG0505:1221: don gcig nyid la 'gyur med do //
NG0505:1222: byang chub sems la 'dzad med pas //
NG0505:1223: 'phrin las nyid la thogs med do //
NG0505:1224: byang chub sems la gnyis med pas //
NG0505:1225: bdud kyis brdzi bar mi nus so //
NG0505:1226: smon pa yid bzhin 'jug pa la //
NG0505:1227: lag len med pa'i sems bskyed ni //
NG0505:1228: lag na yod kyang mi phan pa //
NG0505:1229: dbul mo'i gter bzhin don mi 'byung *//
NG0505:1230: nus pa yod bzhin rang don sgrub //
NG0505:1231: gzhan don mi byed dud 'gror skye //
NG0505:1232: longs spyod yid bzhin tshogs mi sogs //
NG0505:1233: ser snas bcings pas yi dwags skye //
NG0505:1234: chos rgyus yod bzhin chos mi spyod //
NG0505:1235: phyin ci log pas dmyal bar skye //
NG0505:1236: byang chub sems bral bde ba med //
NG0505:1237: de bas byang chub 'jug pa gtso //
NG0505:1239: smon pa bzang yang gnas skabs tsam //
NG0505:1240: blo gros dman pa'i le lo can //
NG0505:1241: thun mong skyabs 'gro nas bzung nas //
NG0505:1242: sngags kyi de nyid man chad kyi //
NG0505:1245: blo dang 'tsham pa'i nus pa yi //
NG0505:1246: bsam pa'i khyad par ji bzhin du //
NG0505:1247: sems can kun gyi skyabs khas blang *//
NG0505:1248: slo dpon che la sems skyed blang *//
NG0505:1249: thams cad mkhyen nyid dbang por bzhugs //
NG0505:1250: 'di nas bar med phyi ma'i mthar //
NG0505:1252: gzhan gyis bar du ma chod pa'i //
NG0505:1253: skas kyi gdang bu lta bu ru //
NG0505:1254: rim pa nyid la 'jug par bya //
NG0505:1255: bla na med pa'i byang chub de //
NG0505:1256: myur du rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0505:1257: dper na rgyal rigs bu tsha ni //
NG0505:1258: dbang bskur thag tu rgyal 'gyur bzhin //
NG0505:1259: byang chub lam rnams skad cig gis //
NG0505:1260: shes rab chen po cig car du //
NG0505:1261: 'jug pa thun mong ma yin pa //
NG0505:1262: bla na med pa'i rgyun du gsungs //
NG0505:1264: thung bar 'dod lam de don rdzogs //
NG0505:1265: 'jug pa rang nyid spyod pa dang *//
NG0505:1266: gzhan la ston cing 'khod pa ni //
NG0505:1267: gnas skabs lam gyi 'jug pa yin //
NG0505:1268: mthar thug sku gnyis don gnyis 'grub //
NG0505:1269: gnyis su med pa byang chub sems //
NG0505:1270: kun la khyab pa chos kyi sku //
NG0505:1271: nyag gcig spros bral 'dus ma byas //
NG0505:1272: thams cad mkhyen pa'i yon tan mtsho //
NG0505:1273: byang chub sems la rang byung ba //
NG0505:1274: lhun grub mi rtog rtog pa can //
NG0505:1275: byang chub lam la gang zhugs pas //
NG0505:1276: dad dang thos dang tshul khrims dang *//
NG0505:1277: khrel yod ngo tsha shes pa dang *//
NG0505:1278: stong dang shes rab rnam pa bdun //
NG0505:1280: mi 'dzad gter du spyi la dgos //
NG0505:1281: snod ma yin la de mi 'byung *//
NG0505:1282: byang chub sems kyi yon tan gang *//
NG0505:1283: sdig sgrib bdud dpung thams cad 'joms //
NG0505:1284: tshogs gnyis dge ba zla ltar 'phel //
NG0505:1285: bum pa bzang po dpag bsam shing *//
NG0505:1287: rang bzhin kun gyi don grub pas //
NG0505:1288: gzugs mchis nam mkha'i mthar mi shog / rjes su dran cing rgya chen spel //
NG0505:1289: spel ba'i tshogs gnyis sogs pa de //
NG0505:1290: bsod nams zang zing mtshan bcas kyi //
NG0505:1291: dge ba zag bcas la brten pa //
NG0505:1292: rang gzhan don gnyis bsgrub pa'o //
NG0505:1293: ye shes mtshan med dmigs med kyis //
NG0505:1294: zag med dge la brten nas su //
NG0505:1295: rang gzhan don du tshogs sog pa //
NG0505:1296: thun mong pha rol phyin pa dang *//
NG0505:1297: spyi dang mthun pa'i sbyin sogs kyi //
NG0505:1298: zhing bsam dngos gsum dag pa yi //
NG0505:1299: dge ba 'khor gsum yongs dag tu //
NG0505:1300: sngo bar byed pa'i tshogs rnams so //
NG0505:1301: thun mong ma yin khyad par ba //
NG0505:1302: sngags kyi smin byed sgor zhugs nas //
NG0505:1303: bskyed rim bsgom pa bsod nams tshogs //
NG0505:1304: rdzogs rim don ni ye shes tshogs //
NG0505:1305: tshogs gnyis spel bas sgrib gnyis byang *//
NG0505:1306: byang chub rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas don //
NG0505:1307: gzhan yang smon pa'i dus nyid du //
NG0505:1308: rang nyid dman pas zhum pa dang *//
NG0505:1309: sems can mangs pas dka' ba dang *//
NG0505:1310: dmu rgod rnams ni 'dul dka' dang *//
NG0505:1313: srog la bab kyang blos mi gtang *//
NG0505:1314: sems can gcig gi bde nyams kyang *//
NG0505:1315: rang gi byang chub sems nyams ni //
NG0505:1316: mang po blos btang nyes pa ni //
NG0505:1317: bskal pa'i mthar yang dag mi 'gyur //
NG0505:1318: slar zhing byang chub nan tan skyed //
NG0505:1319: mchod par 'os pa bslus pa dang *//
NG0505:1320: dge la 'gyod pa skyes pa dang *//
NG0505:1321: sems can g.yo sgyus brid pa dang *//
NG0505:1322: sems bskyed pa dang smad pa dang *//
NG0505:1323: tshul ma yin pa spang bar bya //
NG0505:1324: mchod 'os rnams la bsnyen bskur bstod //
NG0505:1325: sems can thabs kyis dge la bkod //
NG0505:1326: theg mchog dge la yi rang bya //
NG0505:1327: sems bskyed pa la bsngags pa brjod //
NG0505:1328: mi dge spong zhing dge ba la //
NG0505:1329: phra zhib rdul gyi cha nas spyad //
NG0505:1330: ma dad pa yi chos nyan dang *//
NG0505:1331: ma gus pa yi phyag 'tshal dang *//
NG0505:1332: mi spro ba yi mchod pa dang *//
NG0505:1333: mi mos pa yi bstod pa dang *//
NG0505:1334: dge ba nyes pa can yin yang *//
NG0505:1335: ma nus pa la nyes pa med //
NG0505:1336: yang dag lam la gang zhugs pa //
NG0505:1337: spyod pa pha rol phyin mchog nyid //
NG0505:1338: sbyin pa'i ngo bo chags med dge //
NG0505:1339: mtshan nyid yongs su gtong ba ste //
NG0505:1340: dbye ba zang zing mi 'jigs chos /
NG0505:1341: khyad par chos kyi sbyin pa 'phags //
NG0505:1342: mi mthun sar sna rnam par spangs //
NG0505:1343: tshul khrims ngo bo dri med dge //
NG0505:1344: mtshan nyid g.yo sgyu med pa de //
NG0505:1345: dbye ba tshul khrims rnam gsum la //
NG0505:1346: sdom pa dge ba don byed do /
NG0505:1347: khyad par zag med tshul khrims mchog / mi mthun phyogs su bag med yang *//
NG0505:1348: bzod pa'i ngo bo sdang med dge //
NG0505:1349: mtshan nyid 'khrul pa med par bstan //
NG0505:1350: dbye ba sdug bsngal dang du len //
NG0505:1351: ji mi mnyam zhing chos la sems //
NG0505:1352: theg chen mi skrag bzod pa 'phags //
NG0505:1353: mi mthun khong khro spang bar bya //
NG0505:1354: brtson 'grus dge la spro ba la //
NG0505:1355: mtshan nyid le lo med pa ste //
NG0505:1356: dbye ba cha sbyin mthar phyin pa'i //
NG0505:1357: lam mchog chos la brtson pa 'phags //
NG0505:1358: mi mthun snyom las rnam par spang *//
NG0505:1359: bsam gtan ngo bo dge la gnas //
NG0505:1360: mtshan nyid g.yeng ba'i rtog tshogs bral //
NG0505:1361: bde gnas don rab 'byed pa dang *//
NG0505:1362: de bzhin nyid la dmigs pa'o //
NG0505:1363: zung 'jug rnam par mi rtog bzang *//
NG0505:1364: mi mthun rtog pas g.yeng ba spang *//
NG0505:1365: shes rab ngo bo bdag med rtogs //
NG0505:1366: mtshan nyid don rnams rab 'byed pa //
NG0505:1367: dbye ba kun rdzogs don dam shes //
NG0505:1368: zung 'jug thos bsam sgom pa gsum //
NG0505:1369: thabs la mkhas pas bla na med //
NG0505:1370: thabs kyi nang na smin grol mchog / mi mthun phyogs su lhung ba yin //
NG0505:1371: stobs kyi ngo bo spang bya 'joms //
NG0505:1372: mtshan nyid spangs thob yon tan 'dzin //
NG0505:1373: spongs dang thob pa yon tan te //
NG0505:1374: zag med bde thob khyad du 'phags //
NG0505:1375: dman pa'i blo ni mi mthun phyogs //
NG0505:1376: smon lam don ldan dge ba'o //
NG0505:1377: mtshan nyid dge ba chud mi za //
NG0505:1378: dag dang ma dag the tshom gsum //
NG0505:1379: dag pa'i smon la mchog tu bzang *//
NG0505:1382: ye shes ngo bo thams cad mkhyen //
NG0505:1383: mtshan nyid gang yang ma bsgrib pa'o //
NG0505:1384: dbye na gzhi yi ye shes dang *//
NG0505:1385: cha mthun lam gyi ye shes dang *//
NG0505:1386: yon tan rab rdzogs ye shes dang *//
NG0505:1387: thams cad mkhyen pa khyad par 'phags //
NG0505:1388: mi mthun sgrib pa gnyis yin no //
NG0505:1389: bdag nyid spyod cing gzhan la sbyor //
NG0505:1390: spyod pa kun la legs pa brjod //
NG0505:1391: nyams su blangs pa'i don che ni //
NG0505:1392: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i bya ba ru //
NG0505:1393: pha rol phyin bcu'i grangs bstan pa //
NG0505:1394: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson bzhi //
NG0505:1395: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs bya bar dgos //
NG0505:1396: bsam gtan shes rab ye shes tshogs //
NG0505:1397: thabs stobs smon lam ye shes bzhi //
NG0505:1398: theg chen 'jug pa'i khyad la dgos //
NG0505:1399: gzhan drug theg pa chung la yod //
NG0505:1400: thun mong pha rol phyin drug yin //
NG0505:1401: pha rol phyin pa bcu yis su //
NG0505:1402: go rim nges par ma nor bas //
NG0505:1403: sa bcu rdzogs pa'i yon tan thob //
NG0505:1404: thabs mkhas nang gis phar phyin bcu //
NG0505:1405: lus la ma zhen sbyin pa'i mchog / ti la ma nyams tshul khrims te //
NG0505:1406: sdug bsngal mi brdzi bzod pa mchog / yengs pa med pa brtson 'grus la //
NG0505:1407: g.yo ba med pa bsam gtan gnas //
NG0505:1408: 'khrul pa med pa'i shes rab kyis //
NG0505:1409: bde ba chen po thabs kyi mchog / thabs chen pha rol gnyis med stobs //
NG0505:1410: smon lam dbyer med lhan cig skyes //
NG0505:1411: rab byung ye shes 'od po che //
NG0505:1412: srid pa'i mun pa ma lus bsal //
NG0505:1413: dpal ldan dang po'i sangs rgyas so //
NG0505:1414: rgyal ba'i thugs rje'i gzugs sku ni //
NG0505:1415: skye ba med pa'i yig 'bru mchog / a yi dbyings nas rang byung ba //
NG0505:1416: ka sogs nam mkha'i yi ge dang *//
NG0505:1417: tsa la sogs pa rlung gi sgra //
NG0505:1418: ta sogs me la sa sogs chu //
NG0505:1419: la sogs sa yi rang sgra las /
NG0505:1420: khams drug yi ge'i gzugs su ni //
NG0505:1421: sems kyi ri mo bris pa yis //
NG0505:1422: tshig dang don dang glegs bam du //
NG0505:1423: 'gro ba kun gyi don phyir du //
NG0505:1424: rgyal ba'i pha rol phyin bcu tshogs //
NG0505:1425: yi ge 'bri dang mchog sbyin dang *//
NG0505:1426: 'chang dang klog dang kha ton bya //
NG0505:1427: don sems 'chad ci yid la bya //
NG0505:1428: tshul bzhin du ni bsgom pa bcu //
NG0505:1429: bdag gzhan 'di phyi'i don grub bar //
NG0505:1430: byang chub lam gyi spyod pa mchog / shes rab rgyal ba kun gyis gsungs //
NG0505:1431: chos spyod bcu la gang brtson pa //
NG0505:1432: lha dang 'khor lo sgyur ba dang *//
NG0505:1433: mi yi gnas nas byang chub thob //
NG0505:1434: log pas ngan song dbul por 'gyur //
NG0505:1435: sgyur byed bsam pa gtso che'o //
NG0505:1436: byang chub sems dpa' mkhas chen po //
NG0505:1437: gzhan don 'phongs pa sbyin pas bsdu //
NG0505:1438: snyan par smra ba'i thabs kyis bsdu //
NG0505:1439: rigs par mthun pa'i spyod pas bsdu //
NG0505:1440: 'dod pa grub pa'i don gyis bsdu //
NG0505:1441: sems can rnams kyi bsam pa bzhin //
NG0505:1442: ji ltar 'dod mthun spyod pa yi //
NG0505:1443: byang chub sems la rab tu dgod //
NG0505:1444: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa rnams //
NG0505:1447: bslab pa gsum du 'dus par ni //
NG0505:1448: rgyal bas chos kun nang du bstan //
NG0505:1449: lhag pa tshul khrims bslab pa rnams //
NG0505:1450: zag bcas lha mi'i tshul khrims la //
NG0505:1451: zag med bde ba'i don mthong bas //
NG0505:1452: 'phags pa dgyes pa'i tshul khrims yin //
NG0505:1453: lhag pa ting 'dzin bslab pa kun //
NG0505:1454: zhi gnas ting 'dzin rtse gcig pa //
NG0505:1456: lhag mthong ye shes rtog pa ni //
NG0505:1458: lhag pa shes rab bslab pa kun //
NG0505:1460: kun rdzob 'khor ba'i shes rab la //
NG0505:1461: rang bzhin gnas lugs shes pa ni //
NG0505:1462: chos kun khong du chud pa yi //
NG0505:1463: shes rab ye shes chen po yin //
NG0505:1464: ye shes ye shes khyad par che //
NG0505:1465: ye shes ldan pas kun don shes //
NG0505:1466: kun don yon tan gsum gyi bdag / mkhas pa sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang *//
NG0505:1467: 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron //
NG0505:1468: byang chub sems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0505:1469: bde dang sdug bsngal las skyes pa'i //
NG0505:1470: kun rdzob lus la bde bas khyab //
NG0505:1471: bde ba nyid ni sdug bsngal bas //
NG0505:1472: bde ba ma nyams tshul khrims mchog / nyams pas sdug bsngal skyed pa'i gzhi //
NG0505:1473: byang chub sems spangs yon tan bskams //
NG0505:1474: bde chen 'khor lo'i thabs kyis ni //
NG0505:1475: bde ba las ni bde ba skye //
NG0505:1476: kun rdzob kun da lta bu ste //
NG0505:1477: don dam bde ba'i gzugs can du //
NG0505:1478: snang srid kun la khyab pa yi //
NG0505:1479: byang chub sems ni rab tu skyed //
NG0505:1480: thams cad ro snyoms lhan cig skyes //
NG0505:1481: rnam par mi rtog yang dag don //
NG0505:1482: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NG0505:1483: chos dbyings dam pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0505:1484: spros bral thig le nyag gcig dbyings //
NG0505:1485: theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa byang chub
NG0505:1486: lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las
NG0505:1487: // byang chub sems dpa' smon lam gyi mthus 'bras
NG0505:1488: bu 'grub par bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NG0505:1489: // gnas lugs chos nyid cig gis ngang *//
NG0505:1490: ma rig kun rtogs rig pa 'di //
NG0505:1491: tha dad snang ba so sor spyod //
NG0505:1492: skye bo rnams ni rang kha ma //
NG0505:1493: phyi rol pa rnams log par rtogs //
NG0505:1494: nang pa phyogs rtogs yang dag rtogs //
NG0505:1495: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i don gcig la //
NG0505:1496: dbang po'i rim pas so sor go / theg pa'i khyad par 'bras bu dang *//
NG0505:1497: dus ni lta spyod khyad par yin //
NG0505:1498: khams gsum gnas na 'dod pa yi //
NG0505:1499: lha mir bcas pa'i theg pa 'di //
NG0505:1502: tshe 'dir zhen pa'i lta ba la //
NG0505:1503: 'khrul pa'i snang ba yengs med bsgom //
NG0505:1504: spyod pa dge sdig lung ma bstan //
NG0505:1507: sna tshogs nges med sdug bsngal grub //
NG0505:1508: blo ma log na thar mi 'gyur //
NG0505:1512: phyin ci log gi lam la zhugs //
NG0505:1513: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i phung po lnga //
NG0505:1514: 'di phyi bar do thams cad du //
NG0505:1515: gcig pu nyid kyis byas pa yin //
NG0505:1516: thams cad rtag pa nyid du 'dod //
NG0505:1517: mi rtag 'byung ba bzhi po yin //
NG0505:1518: rtag pa'i skyes bu mkha' la sdod //
NG0505:1520: phung po nyid mtshams sbyor ba 'khrul //
NG0505:1521: rtag pa'i skyes bu dkar la 'dril //
NG0505:1522: sems can kun gyi snying dkyil na //
NG0505:1523: bungs dang sbyar ba'i re re yod //
NG0505:1524: de yis thams cad byed pa yin //
NG0505:1525: rtag pa chen po gcig nyid la //
NG0505:1526: dper na nam mkha' gcig nyid la //
NG0505:1527: snod mangs nang du dum bur chad //
NG0505:1528: de bzhin sems can ngar 'dzin gyis //
NG0505:1529: rtags pa dum bur mi rtag chad //
NG0505:1531: bdag nyid rtag pa'i grangs can 'dod //
NG0505:1532: chad par lta bar rgyang 'phen pa //
NG0505:1533: tshe la snga dang phyi ma med //
NG0505:1534: da lta blo bur byung ba yin //
NG0505:1535: dge sdig las dang rnam smin med //
NG0505:1536: sems can sangs rgyas bde sdug med //
NG0505:1537: me shi thal ba rlung khyer bzhin //
NG0505:1538: shi nas ci yang med par lta //
NG0505:1539: gnyis mthun spyad dang dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0505:1540: mchod legs sems can bde legs 'byung *//
NG0505:1542: gcer bu thal bas lus byugs shing *//
NG0505:1543: ral pa'i khur bu 'phreng bas brgyan //
NG0505:1544: mdung thung mi mgo'i lag cha thogs //
NG0505:1545: spyod pa dbyug gu gsum pa dang *//
NG0505:1546: dud 'gro ma yi dka' thub spyod //
NG0505:1547: 'bras bu 'di nas 'phos ma thag / rnam smin rgyu 'bras mi 'dod pas //
NG0505:1548: chad lta mnar med dmyal bar skye //
NG0505:1549: gzhan yang ngan song gnas su lhung *//
NG0505:1550: blo log thar pa thob bam ci //
NG0505:1552: dge ba'i bshes gnyen chos nyan pas //
NG0505:1553: nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa yi //
NG0505:1554: nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga //
NG0505:1555: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NG0505:1556: gang zag bdag tu 'dzin pa de //
NG0505:1557: bdag med tsam zhig ma rtogs pa //
NG0505:1558: chos kyis bdag med ma rtogs pas //
NG0505:1559: phyi rol gzung ba'i yul la ni //
NG0505:1560: rags pa rdzas ni dngos po 'dod //
NG0505:1561: phra ba rdul phran si lu ma //
NG0505:1562: rdul rnams bskor ba'i bar bar na //
NG0505:1563: cha med rdul rnams shong bar 'dod //
NG0505:1564: mdo sde pa yi lta ba de //
NG0505:1565: bye brag smra ba phra rag rdul //
NG0505:1566: rdul phran cha med gcig tu 'dod //
NG0505:1567: gnyis ka 'dzin sems de mi spong *//
NG0505:1568: skad cig cha med phag na mo //
NG0505:1570: rgyu 'bras spang sgrub byed pa yi //
NG0505:1571: shes pa skad cig mi rtag par //
NG0505:1573: spyod pa rang don tshul khrims bsrung *//
NG0505:1574: gzhan gyi don ni mi nus shing *//
NG0505:1575: dur khrod dgon pa shing drung dang *//
NG0505:1576: bla gab med par ji bzhin gnas //
NG0505:1577: phyag dar khrod dang phyis pa //
NG0505:1578: chos gos gsum pa'i gos gyon zhing *//
NG0505:1579: stan gcig bsod snyoms thar chags pa'i //
NG0505:1582: cog pu'i spyod pa la sogs pa //
NG0505:1583: sbyangs pa'i yon tan brtan pa yi //
NG0505:1584: rgyun du zhugs nas dgra bcom par //
NG0505:1587: lus gcig blangs nas phyi ma ni //
NG0505:1589: tha mas skye ba gsum blangs nas //
NG0505:1590: dgra bcom pa yi 'bras bu thob //
NG0505:1591: rang rgyal bskal pa mang po nas //
NG0505:1592: sdug bsngal chos la blo log kyang *//
NG0505:1593: byang chub sems dpa'i g.yeng bas 'jig / rang lus ting 'dzin mes sbyangs nas //
NG0505:1594: sangs rgyas mi 'byon sa phyogs su //
NG0505:1595: smon lam btab nas skyes pa yis //
NG0505:1596: slob dpon med par dur khrod du //
NG0505:1597: shi ba rus la brtag pa yis //
NG0505:1599: shes na lugs bzlog ma rig pa //
NG0505:1600: bkag nas bsgom pa tshe sngon gyi //
NG0505:1601: ting 'dzin ldan pa rang sangs rgyas //
NG0505:1602: gang zag bdag med cher rtogs steng *//
NG0505:1603: gzung yul sems kyi cho 'phrul du //
NG0505:1604: shes kyang sems su ma rig pas //
NG0505:1605: chos kyis bdag med phyed rtogs te //
NG0505:1606: gzung yul bcom pa'i 'dzin sems ni //
NG0505:1607: thun mong phag na tsam du 'dod //
NG0505:1608: don dam stong pa nyid du ni //
NG0505:1610: bsgom par mi sad myos pa 'byung *//
NG0505:1611: spyod pa nyan thos rnams dang mthun //
NG0505:1612: mang po ne tso'i khyu tsam lding *//
NG0505:1613: rang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ni //
NG0505:1614: rab kyis mi tshe nyi shu dang *//
NG0505:1615: 'bring gis drug cu tham pa ni //
NG0505:1616: bse ru lta bur rang sangs rgyas //
NG0505:1617: 'gro don lus kyis rta yin byed //
NG0505:1618: zhi bde chos la blo log pa //
NG0505:1619: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i sems tsam ni //
NG0505:1620: phyogs med bdag med sems rtogs pas /
NG0505:1621: khams gsum 'di dag sems su shes //
NG0505:1622: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad po //
NG0505:1623: rang rig rang gsal nyid du ni //
NG0505:1624: mtshan nyid gsum du 'dus pa ste //
NG0505:1625: chos kun spyi dang bye brag tu //
NG0505:1626: sna tshogs ming btags mtshan mar ltar //
NG0505:1627: tha snyad 'dogs pa kun rtags zhes //
NG0505:1628: ma rig 'du byed rkyen gyis skyes //
NG0505:1629: rang bzhin skye med gzhan dbang ste //
NG0505:1630: de rnams rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NG0505:1631: dbyer med ci yang 'grub med don //
NG0505:1632: yongs grub ces su bshad pa la //
NG0505:1633: phyi rol snang ba dkar dmar rnams //
NG0505:1634: rnam pa sgyu ma tsam du ni //
NG0505:1635: rnam bden so sor bden par 'dod //
NG0505:1636: don dam shes pa'i yul las 'das //
NG0505:1637: de yang dri bcas dri med pa //
NG0505:1638: sems la ma dag dag par 'dod //
NG0505:1639: rnam rdzun snang ba dkar dmar kun //
NG0505:1640: phyi rol rdzun la nang du rdzun //
NG0505:1641: dngos med 'khrul pa'i snang ba la //
NG0505:1642: sna tshogs du mar snang ba yang *//
NG0505:1643: yang dag bde shes gcig las med //
NG0505:1644: dper na chu nang zla ba bzhin //
NG0505:1645: gcig las cho 'phrul sna tshogs pa //
NG0505:1646: gsal byed gzhan las ma bltos par //
NG0505:1647: mtshan nyid gsum ga rang la tshang *//
NG0505:1648: bsgom pa byang chub sems nyid la //
NG0505:1651: pha rol phyin pa bcu la spyod //
NG0505:1652: 'bras bu rang rig rang gsal du //
NG0505:1653: gzhan las ma byung byang chub 'dod //
NG0505:1654: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos gsungs gang *//
NG0505:1655: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NG0505:1656: chos can kun rdzob bden pa dang *//
NG0505:1657: chos nyid don dam bden pa la //
NG0505:1658: mtha' bral gshis kyis dbu ma 'o //
NG0505:1659: kun rdzob yang dag sangs rgyas de //
NG0505:1660: ma rtogs sgrib phyir kun rdzob ste //
NG0505:1661: thog ma bar dang mthar bsgrangs pa'i //
NG0505:1662: 'khrul pa'i snang ngor bden pa la //
NG0505:1663: yang dag log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis //
NG0505:1664: kun rdzob rten 'brel chos rnams kun //
NG0505:1665: rgyu 'bras mi bslu thad kar bden //
NG0505:1666: mthun par snang zhing don byed nus //
NG0505:1667: rang bzhin brtags na bden pa de //
NG0505:1668: rang gi sems su shes pa yi //
NG0505:1669: bden rdzun grol ba yang dag yin //
NG0505:1670: sgyu ma smig sgyu chu zla la //
NG0505:1671: rdzun la bden par gzung ba yis //
NG0505:1672: bslus pa log pa'i kun rdzob ste //
NG0505:1675: chos rnams kun gyi chos nyid don //
NG0505:1676: dam pa'i rang bzhin 'gyur med de //
NG0505:1677: bslus pa med pa yang dag pa //
NG0505:1678: don dam pa yi bden pa zhes //
NG0505:1679: rnam grangs stong nyid du ma rnams //
NG0505:1680: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos nyid kyi //
NG0505:1681: bye brag phye ba'i bden pa yin //
NG0505:1682: rnam grangs ma yin spros dang bral //
NG0505:1683: dus gsum 'gyur med mnyam nyid yin //
NG0505:1684: de rnams rang rgyud 'dod pa la //
NG0505:1685: snang ba kun rdzob tsam du ni //
NG0505:1686: sgyu ma tsam gyis bden par 'dod //
NG0505:1687: don dam du ni snang ba 'di //
NG0505:1688: sgyu ma tsam yang med pa yi //
NG0505:1689: nam mkha' lta bur mi dmigs kyis //
NG0505:1691: 'thab bral gshis kyi dbu ma ni //
NG0505:1692: yod dang med pa'i mtha' bral zhing *//
NG0505:1693: mtha' gnyis mi gnyis mnyam nyid 'dod //
NG0505:1694: phyi ma'i dus na 'di nyid la //
NG0505:1695: gcig dang bral ba la sogs pa'i //
NG0505:1696: rang gis kha ni mi ches shing *//
NG0505:1697: gzhan gzhan grub mtha' sun 'byin pa'i //
NG0505:1698: thal 'gyur ba yi dbu ma ni /
NG0505:1699: khas len bral ba'i lta ba 'byung *//
NG0505:1700: stong nyid snying rje'i bsgom lo can //
NG0505:1701: spyod pa pha rol phyin sogs la //
NG0505:1702: 'bras bu myur na grangs med gsum //
NG0505:1703: zhen pa'i chos la dus med do //
NG0505:1704: sngon bsgyur dbang thob sngon byung du //
NG0505:1705: sa bcu'i lam la rab gnas pa //
NG0505:1706: thub pa chen pos zab pa'i gzung *//
NG0505:1707: dngos dang stong pa'i zhen pa las //
NG0505:1708: ldog phyir rig pa 'dzin pa ni //
NG0505:1709: bdag med chos rnams thams cad kun //
NG0505:1710: kun rdzob bdag med dam tshig la //
NG0505:1711: bran bzhin dmigs pa'i 'og min nas //
NG0505:1712: ye shes sems dpa' rgyal ba'i tshul //
NG0505:1713: bris shing yid kyis dmigs pa la //
NG0505:1714: spyan drangs dbang bskur bzhugs gsol zhu //
NG0505:1715: de la gtsang ma'i mchod pa phul //
NG0505:1716: dngos grub de yis thob pa ni //
NG0505:1717: kri ya ba yi lta ba'i yin //
NG0505:1718: sgom pa don gyi lha drug la //
NG0505:1721: 'bras bu mi tshe bdun tsam na //
NG0505:1723: yo ga dam tshig sems dpa' ni //
NG0505:1724: rang lus bsgom pa g.yog por lta //
NG0505:1725: ye shes sems dpa' dpon gyi tshul //
NG0505:1726: spyan drangs rang la bstim nas su //
NG0505:1727: sngags dang phyag rgya bsgrub byas pas //
NG0505:1728: phyag rgya ma bkrol bar du ni //
NG0505:1729: ye shes sems dpa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0505:1730: rang nyid de bzhin gnas 'gyur lta //
NG0505:1731: byang chub lnga yi lha bsgom zhing *//
NG0505:1732: mchod yon sngags dang phyag rgya yis //
NG0505:1733: spyod pas tshogs rdzogs dngos grub len //
NG0505:1735: mi tshe gsum gyis thob par 'dod //
NG0505:1736: u pa lta ba yo ga la //
NG0505:1737: spyod pa kri ya dag dang mtshungs //
NG0505:1739: mi tshe skye ba lnga yis thob //
NG0505:1740: kun brtags phyi nas re ba'i phyir //
NG0505:1741: sngags ni phyi pa zhes su brjod //
NG0505:1742: snang srid chos kun bskyed pa yi //
NG0505:1743: rig pa rang gsal rdo rje 'di //
NG0505:1744: dngos 'dzin thabs kyis dgrol ba'i phyir //
NG0505:1745: kun rdzob lta ba'i sku ru bskyed //
NG0505:1746: dngos med stong pa dag pa'i don //
NG0505:1747: lha kun don dam spros med bdag / shes rab rig pas rtogs pa yis //
NG0505:1748: snang ba lha yi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0505:1749: thabs dang shes rab sgom pa ni //
NG0505:1750: ma ha yo ga'i lta ba la //
NG0505:1751: dam tshig ye shes gnyis med du //
NG0505:1752: sgom pa lha dang ma bral ba //
NG0505:1753: dkyil 'khor chen por mchod pa la //
NG0505:1754: spyod pa 'phrin las rnam bzhi bsgrub //
NG0505:1755: 'bras bu skye ba gcig la ni //
NG0505:1756: mi skye'i chos la spyod pa yid //
NG0505:1757: rdo rje dbyings kyi yon tan thob //
NG0505:1758: thabs mang dka' med bslabs pa ste //
NG0505:1759: dngos dang dngos med thams cad kun //
NG0505:1760: skye med dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NG0505:1762: lha sku ma bskyed rdzogs pa yi //
NG0505:1763: dran pa tsam gyis snang ba 'di //
NG0505:1764: sku dang ye shes zhing du gsal //
NG0505:1765: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su med //
NG0505:1766: stong pa de nyid 'bras bu yin //
NG0505:1767: bsgom pa'i ting 'dzin rnam gsum las //
NG0505:1768: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi sgor zhugs na //
NG0505:1769: spyod pa ta na g+ha na yis //
NG0505:1770: tshe 'di nyid la mchod thob pa //
NG0505:1771: a nu yo ga'i rnal 'byor yin //
NG0505:1772: ye nas snang srid snod bcud kun //
NG0505:1773: ma skyes rang byung chos nyid mkha' //
NG0505:1774: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin la //
NG0505:1775: sangs rgyas chos kun ma lus rdzogs //
NG0505:1776: lhun grub 'gyur med rdo rje gdan //
NG0505:1777: don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal //
NG0505:1778: yang dag rdzogs pa der sangs rgyas //
NG0505:1779: sprul pa po rnams 'dir sangs rgyas //
NG0505:1781: thams cad gcig gyur nan tan nyid //
NG0505:1782: rdzogs pa chos nyid dag pa ste //
NG0505:1783: bsam brjod bral ba'i ye shes la //
NG0505:1784: 'bras bu gdod nas lhun gyis grub //
NG0505:1785: mi rtag chos rnams rtag par zad //
NG0505:1786: kun tu bzang po kun bdag nyid //
NG0505:1787: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NG0505:1788: don gnyis ldan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0505:1791: sangs rgyas chos kun mnyam nyid las //
NG0505:1792: dmus long g.yang la bskyur ba bzhin //
NG0505:1793: phyin ci log tu khrid pa rnams //
NG0505:1794: log pa'i steng du yang log bsnan //
NG0505:1795: log lta sde drug rjes 'brang ba //
NG0505:1796: las kyi sgrib pa 'thug po bsags //
NG0505:1797: mi shes long ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NG0505:1798: bskal par mun pa'i gnas su 'khyams //
NG0505:1799: sangs rgyas che ba'i don 'dod phyir //
NG0505:1801: 'phags pa ma yin de ltar min //
NG0505:1802: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa yin //
NG0505:1803: phyin ci log ste sems dpa' yang *//
NG0505:1804: spangs pas thob pa'i yon tan te //
NG0505:1805: thabs la mkhas pa'i skyes bu yin //
NG0505:1806: dman dang byis pas de mi shes //
NG0505:1807: ma shes gzung 'dzin mtha' la zhen //
NG0505:1809: de bzhin nyid rtogs kun 'dod kyang *//
NG0505:1810: ma rtogs 'bras bu so sor thob //
NG0505:1811: theg pa'i mtha' la thug med pas //
NG0505:1812: theg chen lam la ma zhugs na //
NG0505:1813: nyan thos rang rgyal theg pa yang *//
NG0505:1814: blo dman so so'i skye bo rnams //
NG0505:1815: lam la drang ba'i thabs tsam la //
NG0505:1816: yang dag lam gyi gegs yin te //
NG0505:1818: bskal pa'i bar du lam la bsgribs //
NG0505:1819: phal cher mu mtha' med par sgrim //
NG0505:1820: dmyal ba gtan gyi gegs ma yin //
NG0505:1821: nyan thos theg pa gtan gyi gegs //
NG0505:1822: 'ga' zhig rang gnas byang chub de //
NG0505:1823: sangs rgyas byin rlabs 'od kyis bskul //
NG0505:1824: theg chen chos la 'jug srid kyang *//
NG0505:1825: dper na chu rgal lan cig la //
NG0505:1826: rje bcangs gnyis su mi byed bzhin //
NG0505:1827: byang chub sems gnyis lam la ni //
NG0505:1828: da lta sngon du 'jug par bya //
NG0505:1829: phyi ma'i yid smon lag rdum mda' /
NG0505:1830: kha tsam tshig las don la dka' //
NG0505:1831: de bas da lta don 'di bsgrubs //
NG0505:1834: gol 'chug med pa'i lam chen la //
NG0505:1835: gsang sngags pha rol phyin pa gnyis //
NG0505:1836: bsgrub bya'i don du gcig pa na //
NG0505:1837: gnyis su bstan pa don ci yod //
NG0505:1838: mi gcig so sor song ba ni //
NG0505:1839: gcig la dgos pa med par 'gyur //
NG0505:1840: de don gcig par mgon por gsungs //
NG0505:1842: 'ga' zhig lam rtags sos dal bar //
NG0505:1843: thag rings lam la bskor nas 'gro //
NG0505:1845: nye ba'i gsang lam gcad nas 'gro //
NG0505:1846: de gnyis lam gyi khyad las su //
NG0505:1847: bsleb dus don 'go gcig pa bzhin //
NG0505:1848: rim gyis cig car don yang de'o //
NG0505:1849: mos pa'i 'dun pa so so yin //
NG0505:1850: lam gyis mi mthun khyad par che //
NG0505:1851: phar phyin dang po'i tshogs lam nas //
NG0505:1852: sems can don du sems bskyed nas //
NG0505:1853: sbyor lam drod rtse bzod pa dang *//
NG0505:1854: chos mchog nas ni mthong lam bar //
NG0505:1855: grangs med gcig gis lam sbyangs pas //
NG0505:1856: mthong lam slob pa'i zung 'jug gis //
NG0505:1858: nyid bden pa'i don mthong bas //
NG0505:1859: rab tu dga' ba'i sa non te //
NG0505:1860: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis 'char //
NG0505:1861: de nas sgom lam sa brgyad par //
NG0505:1862: gong nas gong du 'phel ba yi //
NG0505:1863: grangs med gcig la mi slob pa'i //
NG0505:1864: sgom lam yon tan phyir mi ldog / grangs med gcig tu bsgoms pa las //
NG0505:1866: sa bcu mthar phyin yon tan rdzogs //
NG0505:1868: bcu gcig kun tu 'od chen po //
NG0505:1869: bla ma sngags kyi lam du ni //
NG0505:1870: slob ma yongs su smin byed pa'i //
NG0505:1871: slob ma rang rig bdag nyid che //
NG0505:1872: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kun lhags nas //
NG0505:1873: rang rig ye shes mngon sum du //
NG0505:1874: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NG0505:1875: ston pa yongs su grol byed pa'i //
NG0505:1876: dbang bskur dgos pas gsang sngags mchog / de med sangs rgyas mi 'gyur bar //
NG0505:1877: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dbang bskur ni //
NG0505:1878: de ltar sa yi yon tan brtags //
NG0505:1879: tshon rtsi ri mo sna tshogs pa //
NG0505:1880: ri mo mkhan gyis byas pa las //
NG0505:1881: gzhan nas 'byung ba ma yin bzhin //
NG0505:1882: rang gi sems kyis byas pa yis //
NG0505:1883: ting nge 'dzin gyi rang snang la //
NG0505:1884: gzhan gyi snang bar 'byung ba dka' //
NG0505:1885: byung yang dper na rmi lam du //
NG0505:1886: ngo mtshar can gyi mchod rten la //
NG0505:1887: mas gyis rim pas 'dzegs pa yis //
NG0505:1888: gdugs kyi steng du bslebs tsa na //
NG0505:1889: gnyid sad bden med 'gyur ba bzhin //
NG0505:1890: gnas skabs lam gyi rtags tsam yin //
NG0505:1891: mthar thug don la yod med 'dra //
NG0505:1892: lam der sngags kyis ma zhugs pas //
NG0505:1893: de yi ting 'dzin ma sbyangs don //
NG0505:1894: sa bcu'i rtags rnams ma byung yang *//
NG0505:1895: lam gyi bgrod pa khyad par med //
NG0505:1896: byung yang sngags kyi lam stegs tsam //
NG0505:1897: rim skyed pa yi chos lugs yin //
NG0505:1898: sngags kyi lam ni bla ma la //
NG0505:1899: brten cing mos pa tshogs kyi lam //
NG0505:1900: bka' bzhin bsgrub pas byin rlabs zhugs //
NG0505:1901: nyams len shes pa sbyor ba lam //
NG0505:1902: snang srid spros bral lha yi sku //
NG0505:1903: bskyed rim bsgom pa mthong ba'i lam //
NG0505:1904: ba spu gcig gi steng du yang *//
NG0505:1905: lha sku 'bum phrag bskyed nus pa //
NG0505:1906: yon tan brgya phrag mang po'i mchog / rang gi sems kyi rnam 'phrul yin //
NG0505:1907: pha rol phyin la de med de //
NG0505:1908: sngags kyi lam la 'byung ba yin //
NG0505:1909: rdzogs rim shes pa bsgom pa lam //
NG0505:1910: dbang rdzogs mthar thug phyag rgya che //
NG0505:1911: tshe gcig 'di la mngon sum du //
NG0505:1912: cig car rtogs pa sngags kyi lam //
NG0505:1913: don gcig lam la mi mthun pa //
NG0505:1914: shel sgong dag pa gzhi ma yin /
NG0505:1915: kha dog gang bstan der 'gyur yang *//
NG0505:1916: shel gyi don la 'gyur med bzhin //
NG0505:1917: gnas skabs lam snang mi mthun yang *//
NG0505:1918: mthar thug gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NG0505:1919: chos dbyings ye shes snying po ni //
NG0505:1920: lhun grub don du dbyer med gcig / theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NG0505:1921: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i chos //
NG0505:1924: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa //
NG0505:1925: ye shes mig gcig dri ma med //
NG0505:1926: mkhyen pa'i ye shes zhing khams mthong *//
NG0505:1927: ma btsal lhun grub e ma ho //
NG0505:1928: theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa byang chub
NG0505:1929: lam gyi rgyud chen po nam mkha' dang mnyam pa
NG0505:1930: las // 'jug pa'i lam theg pa'i bye brag bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o ///
NG0505:1931: / byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de //
NG0505:1932: lus kyi tshul gyis rnam par dag / lus ni rtsa yi dra bas te //
NG0505:1933: gzugs dang kha dog rnam pa can //
NG0505:1934: rtsa skyed lus kyang bskyed par byed //
NG0505:1935: rtsa gud lus kyang nyams par byed //
NG0505:1937: dran pa g.yo zhing ldeg par byed //
NG0505:1938: rlung las khams skyed bde sdug dang *//
NG0505:1939: rtag dang mi rtag de yis byas //

NG0505:1945: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de //

NG0505:1948: byang chub sems ni gcig nyid la //

NG0505:2704: sems can sangs rgyas zhal der mjal //
NG0505:2705: gnyis med rtogs na de bzhin gshegs //
NG0505:2706: phyag rgya chen po'i lha sku ni //
NG0505:2707: mang por bsgoms dang gcig tu 'dra //
NG0505:2708: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs ye shes 'thob /
NG0505:2709: kha zas kun la mchod sbyin bya //
NG0505:2710: bskal pa bye ba phrag brgyar yang *//
NG0505:2711: bsod nams yon tan brjod mi nus //
NG0505:2712: the tshom thams cad rnam par sel //
NG0505:2713: sgrib pa kun las nges par grol //
NG0505:2714: chu bo rgya mtsho kun las brgal //
NG0505:2715: chos kun rnam par khong du chud //
NG0505:2716: bsod nams phung po rnam par 'phel //
NG0505:2717: ye shes phung po rnam par thob //
NG0505:2718: sems can rnams ni rnam sbyong ba'i //
NG0505:2719: mgon po sems can kun don du //
NG0505:2720: de yi yon tan dpag par dka' //
NG0505:2721: tshogs bsags pas kyang tshogs mi thob //
NG0505:2722: tshogs ma bsags pas tshogs mi thob //
NG0505:2723: de bas tshogs kun gong du spel //
NG0505:2725: theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtog pa byang chub
NG0505:2726: lam gyi rgyud mchog nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las
NG0505:2727: // bsod nams tshogs bsags pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //    // bsod nams tshogs ni bsags byas te //
NG0505:2729: pas mtshan ma bcas pa la //
NG0505:2730: ye shes tshogs ni thob byas te //
NG0505:2731: dmigs med mtshan ma grol ba'o //
NG0505:2732: dge sdig gnyis kyis spang blang la //
NG0505:2734: rgyu 'bras gnyis la zhen pa yis //
NG0505:2735: stong par shes pa ye shes yin //
NG0505:2736: gzung ba'i yul ni mi 'dod la //
NG0505:2737: 'dzin sems mi dmigs theg dman yin //
NG0505:2738: gzung 'dzin gnyis su mi rtogs pa'i //
NG0505:2739: snang bar shes pa ye shes yin //
NG0505:2740: snang ba sems su 'dod pa ni //
NG0505:2741: chos kyis bdag 'dzin shes bya ste //
NG0505:2742: shes dang shes bya'i yul 'das pas //
NG0505:2743: rang bzhin rtogs pa ye shes tshogs //
NG0505:2744: rnam par mi rtog bdag med chos //

NG0505:2746: yang dag mthong na rnam grol yin //
NG0505:2747: sems can kun gyi bde sdug de //
NG0505:2748: dge sdig gnyis kyi rgyu 'bras la //
NG0505:2749: rgyu 'bras gnyis la ma chog pa'i //
NG0505:2750: bden med rtogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0505:2751: las kyi sgrib pa dag pa ni //
NG0505:2752: nyan thos rang rgyal ye shes tshogs //
NG0505:2753: 'khor bar mi ldog yon tan thob //
NG0505:2754: dug gsum 'khor ba'i rtsa lag de //
NG0505:2755: gdod nas ma skyes stong pa nyid //
NG0505:2756: ma 'gags ngo bo rnam pa ni //
NG0505:2757: rten 'brel shar ba'i rang bzhin la //
NG0505:2758: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba yi //
NG0505:2759: sems su rtogs pa'i chos nyid la //
NG0505:2760: nyon mongs sgrib pa med pa de //
NG0505:2761: byang chub sems dpa'i ye shes tshogs //
NG0505:2762: phung po lnga ni rigs lnga la //
NG0505:2763: 'byung ba lnga ni bskyed pa'i yum //
NG0505:2764: nyon mongs lnga ni ye shes lnga //
NG0505:2765: snang tshad byang chub sems su rtogs //
NG0505:2766: theg glan phyir mi ldog pa'i chos //
NG0505:2767: bden pa'i yon tan gong du thob //
NG0505:2768: sems dang sems byung skyed byed pa'i //
NG0505:2769: kun gzhi ma bcos rang grol la //
NG0505:2771: stong pa mi dmigs mngon sum du //
NG0505:2772: bsod nams tshogs las byung ba yi //
NG0505:2774: ma shes blo'i yul du ni //
NG0505:2775: kun rdzob bden pa mngon sum pa //
NG0505:2776: sems can rnams kyi rgyud la gsal //
NG0505:2777: rig cing rtogs pa'i dus nyid na //
NG0505:2779: mya ngan 'das pa mngon sum du //
NG0505:2780: bcos ma ma yin gnas lugs la //
NG0505:2781: rang rig ye shes dngos su gsal //
NG0505:2782: 'di la gsal cha ci yang med //
NG0505:2783: gzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NG0505:2784: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid de //
NG0505:2785: rang 'byung ye shes sangs rgyas kyi //
NG0505:2786: yon tan tshogs ni rdzogs par 'gyur //
NG0505:2787: ye shes ye shes khyad par las //
NG0505:2788: ye shes ldan pa yod min shes //
NG0505:2789: tshogs gnyis bsod nams bsags pa las //
NG0505:2790: 'bras bu kun rdzob bden pa ru //
NG0505:2791: thabs mkhas gzugs kyi sku ru byung *//
NG0505:2793: de yi ye shes tshogs gnyis la //
NG0505:2794: 'bras bu don dam bden pa ru //
NG0505:2795: shes rab ye shes chos kyi sku //
NG0505:2796: thams cad ma bcos lhun grub tu //
NG0505:2797: rang grol ngo bo nyid kyis dag / dag pa gzhan gyis rnam grol @#//
NG0505:2799: rang gis rang nyid shes te byos //
NG0505:2800: 'di ni byin brlabs rim pa yis //
NG0505:2801: gzhi nas lam du mthar thug pa //
NG0505:2802: byas pa med par rang shar du //
NG0505:2803: so sor rang rig spyod yul du //
NG0505:2804: kun mkhyen ye shes de lta bu //
NG0505:2805: gdod nas lhun grub 'gyur med kyang *//
NG0505:2806: sprin bral nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bzhin //
NG0505:2807: tshogs gnyis las byung rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NG0505:2808: gzhan nas ma 'tshol rang la ltos //
NG0505:2809: rang byung ye shes tshogs kyi mchog / mi 'gyur kun 'gro khyab pa po //
NG0505:2810: khyab bdag ye shes lnga dang ldan //
NG0505:2811: dbyer med thig le gcig tu shes //
NG0505:2812: sdong po gcig shes yal ga ni //
NG0505:2813: sna tshogs tshul gcig shes pa bzhin //
NG0505:2814: chos kyi dbyings la rtogs pa yi //
NG0505:2816: rnam pa sna tshogs du ma rnams //
NG0505:2817: mtshan nyid ma 'gags so so yang *//
NG0505:2818: gdod nas gnas lugs spros dang bral //
NG0505:2819: rang bzhin gcig tu shes pa ni //
NG0505:2820: ye shes tshogs zhes tshig tu bstan //
NG0505:2821: don gyis gnas lugs rnam dag dpal //
NG0505:2822: dpal ldan 'byor pa kun byed do //
NG0505:2824: chung yang sdig pa zil gyis gnon //
NG0505:2825: nyan thos rang rgyal 'byor pa yis //
NG0505:2826: dman yang 'jig rten zil gyis gnon //
NG0505:2827: byang chub sems kyi 'byor ba yis //
NG0505:2828: theg dman zhi bde zil gyis gnon //
NG0505:2829: sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'byor ba yis //
NG0505:2830: srin bu me khyer sgron me dang *//
NG0505:2831: skar ma zla ba'i 'od zer kun //
NG0505:2832: nyi ma'i 'od kyis mnan pa bzhin //
NG0505:2833: theg pa thams cad zil gnon cing *//
NG0505:2834: rang gi 'od kyis khyab par byed //
NG0505:2836: theg chen ye shes gcig gi ngang *//
NG0505:2837: 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje'i gdan //
NG0505:2838: thams cad mkhyen pa der sangs rgyas //
NG0505:2839: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa byang chub
NG0505:2840: lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las
NG0505:2841: // ye shes kyi tshogs skyed pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0505:2842: / srid dang zhi bar gnas pa'i chos //
NG0505:2843: thams cad sems kyi gzugs brnyan te //
NG0505:2844: shes dang shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0505:2845: dag dang ma dag gnyis su bstan //
NG0505:2846: bdag srid pa yi gnas 'di na //
NG0505:2847: rnam shes sna tshogs gzugs don can //
NG0505:2848: mi shes shes pa sna tshogs ni //
NG0505:2849: dper na spre'u mdud pa bzhin //
NG0505:2851: dag pa shes rab thabs ldan rnams //
NG0505:2852: sngags shes btson las thar pa bzhin //
NG0505:2853: shes bya'i chos kyi rang bzhin rnams //
NG0505:2854: shes pa'i 'khor ba las grol te //
NG0505:2855: mya ngan 'das pa shes rab yin //
NG0505:2856: thabs med shes rab bral bas na //
NG0505:2857: theg pa dman dang 'khor bar ltung *//
NG0505:2858: grol dang ma grol lam zhugs pa'i //
NG0505:2859: theg pa'i khyad par shes rab bstan //
NG0505:2860: srid gcig sems kyi glong 'di na //
NG0505:2861: gnas lugs shes bya'i babs las su //
NG0505:2862: phyi nang snod bcud kha dog dbyibs //
NG0505:2863: che chung ring thung gzugs can @#//
NG0505:2865: dang po rgyud las lhun grub pa'i //
NG0505:2866: ma bcos pa yi bzo ru shes //
NG0505:2867: de nyid bcos na 'jig par rig / yod la yod du spel ba dang *//
NG0505:2868: med la med du stong pa dang *//
NG0505:2869: stong pa nyid la dngos por skyed //
NG0505:2870: dngos po nyid las stong par stong *//
NG0505:2871: bde la sdug dang sdug la bde //
NG0505:2872: yin la min dang min la yin //
NG0505:2873: gcig las ma skyes mang 'dus gcig / bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa dang *//
NG0505:2874: shes dang ma shes rnam 'gyur sogs //
NG0505:2875: dus de'i rkyen des byas pa yis //
NG0505:2876: rgyu med sems kyi bzo ru shes //
NG0505:2877: rkyen de dag ni 'jig par rig / rgyu dang rkyen gnyis 'dzom pa las //
NG0505:2878: dbyibs dang kha dog gzugs brnyan kun //
NG0505:2879: rgyu'i dpe yis mtshon nas su //
NG0505:2880: legs nyes lag gis byas pa'i bzo //
NG0505:2881: mkhas pas nan chags yin par shes //
NG0505:2882: gzugs dang bral na 'jig par rig / des ltar bzo'i gnas rnams la //
NG0505:2883: rgyu'i rgyu las dpe byas shing *//
NG0505:2884: rkyen gyis bzo'i rnam pa bsgyur //
NG0505:2885: lag gis bzo la mkhas par sbyangs //
NG0505:2886: gang yin don la ma rmongs pa'i //
NG0505:2887: bzo'i rig pa gtan la dbab //
NG0505:2888: gnas lugs gshis kyi rang sgra de //
NG0505:2889: bye brag 'byung ba'i rang brtsal du //
NG0505:2890: sa la lci ba brjid kyi sgra //
NG0505:2891: chu las 'dar ba rlan gyi sgra //
NG0505:2892: me las 'chog pa drod kyi sgra //
NG0505:2893: rlung la g.yo ba shugs kyi sgra //
NG0505:2894: nam mkha' dbugs kyi stong pa'i sgra //
NG0505:2895: rang bzhin nyid du gnas pa la //
NG0505:2896: 'byung ba chen po sgra che ba //
NG0505:2897: rkyen gyis stobs kyis sna tshogs sgrog / de'ang 'byung ba gzhan rkyen dang *//
NG0505:2898: rang gi sgra skad thun mong 'byung *//
NG0505:2899: sgra don gnyis po gcig tu shes //
NG0505:2900: sgra don log pa 'byung mi srid //
NG0505:2901: srid par gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams /
NG0505:2902: khams drug 'dus pa'i rang gzugs ni //
NG0505:2903: las dang nyon mongs nyer len gyis //
NG0505:2904: rigs drug so so'i lus la ni //
NG0505:2905: de dang de'i sgra skad rnams //
NG0505:2907: sgra des don rnams thad kar go / rang sgra mi shes sems can med //
NG0505:2908: sgra don rtogs na 'phags pa yin //
NG0505:2909: ma rig pa yis de mi rtogs //
NG0505:2910: shes rig cha dang ldan pa yis //
NG0505:2911: don rnams tshig gis rtogs pa'i phyir //
NG0505:2912: rigs drug so so'i sgra skad rnams //
NG0505:2913: tshig gis don kun rig pa la //
NG0505:2914: bsgyur byed tshig gi sgra brjod pas //
NG0505:2915: so dang mchu dang gre ba rkan //
NG0505:2916: lce'i bsgyur byed tshogs pa las //
NG0505:2917: sgra dang tshig tu gsal ba yin //
NG0505:2918: de yis don kun rig pas na //
NG0505:2919: sgra tshad rig pa'i shes rab kyis //
NG0505:2920: sgra dang ldan pa rnams kyi mchog / shes bya gcig la kun spyod kyang *//
NG0505:2921: sgra mi shes pas don mi rtogs //
NG0505:2922: de phyir sgra la brten pa'i tshig / tshig la brten nas don 'byung bas //
NG0505:2923: sgra tshig don la mkhas par bslab //
NG0505:2924: gnas rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NG0505:2925: sgra med tshig la spro ba kun //
NG0505:2926: don med mun pa'i dbyug bskor de //
NG0505:2927: thog tu phebs pa shin tu dka' //
NG0505:2930: nyon mongs las kyi rkyen dbang gis //
NG0505:2931: nad rigs gso bya mang yod rnams //
NG0505:2932: mdor bsdus rnam pa gsum yin te //
NG0505:2933: brgyad khri bzhi stong nyon mongs rnams //
NG0505:2934: rtsa ba dug gsum las gyur pa'i //
NG0505:2935: sems kyis nad kun rnam par skyed //
NG0505:2936: khams gsum gnas pa'i zug rngu la //
NG0505:2937: rang gi gnyen por rang nyid che //
NG0505:2939: de bzhin zhe sdang zhe sdang 'joms //
NG0505:2940: gti mug mang po tshogs pa yis //
NG0505:2941: rten 'brel thabs la mkhas pas sel //
NG0505:2942: nad do cog gi sgra che rnams //
NG0505:2943: bdag med rtogs pa'i sman mchog gis //
NG0505:2944: zug rngu 'byin cing bla na med //
NG0505:2945: bde ba chen por 'tshe ba'i gnas //
NG0505:2946: chags sdang las skyes 'byung lus la //
NG0505:2947: nyon mongs rgyu skyed 'bras bu nad //
NG0505:2948: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad skyed pas //
NG0505:2949: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pas te //
NG0505:2951: 'jugs pa sha rgyas lpags la gram //
NG0505:2952: rtsa la 'khyug dang rus pa zhen //
NG0505:2953: don la babs dang snod du ltung *//
NG0505:2954: smin rtags zer zug 'gying can dang *//
NG0505:2955: ldang lugs rnam pa gsum la ni //
NG0505:2956: rlung gi gyen la bad kan 'thur //
NG0505:2957: mkhris pa thad kar ldang ba la //
NG0505:2958: gso thabs bsil drod sman dang spyad //
NG0505:2959: mkhas pa nad med lus zungs skyed //
NG0505:2960: rnam rtog rkyen las gyur pa'i nad //
NG0505:2961: sgra yi nad dang gdon gyi nad //
NG0505:2962: rnam par rtog pa yid kyi nad //
NG0505:2963: rnam rtog nad la rnam rtog gi / log non zlog pa gdam ngag yin //
NG0505:2964: gso thabs de yi dmigs pa po //
NG0505:2965: rnam par rtog med ngang gis grol //
NG0505:2966: sman pa che mchog gtso bo ni //
NG0505:2967: gso ba'i gnas rnams kun gyi mchog /  drang srong che dgus mchod cing bstod //
NG0505:2968: gso dpyad yan lag kun tu 'phros //
NG0505:2970: thog mar srid pa sems kyi mkha' //
NG0505:2971: dmyal ba srid pa'i bar 'di ru //
NG0505:2972: mthing dkar ser dmar ljang 'od las //
NG0505:2973: 'byung ba chen po lnga byung ste //
NG0505:2975: 'byung ba rang gdangs stobs che'i dus //
NG0505:2976: bskal pa dang po rlung gis skyed //
NG0505:2977: dngos med dbyibs su chu yis 'chags //
NG0505:2978: bar du sa yis dngos por gnas //
NG0505:2979: tha mar me yis dngos po 'jig / skabs su rlung gis stongs par byed //
NG0505:2980: de bzhin phyi nang gzhan gsum cig / 'byung ba gcig gis gcig skyen ba'i //
NG0505:2981: snyoms dang ma snyoms 'phel zad las //
NG0505:2983: bar gyi bskal chung nyi shu bzhi //
NG0505:2985: 'byung ba chen po bzhi las med //
NG0505:2986: bzhi po nam mkha'i ngang du gcig / nam mkha' sems kyi rtog pa yin //
NG0505:2987: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NG0505:2988: 'jig rten khams kyi phyogs brtsi ba //
NG0505:2989: dang po chu la chags pa'i rtags //
NG0505:2990: shar phyogs chu la lho phyogs sa //
NG0505:2991: nub phyogs me la byang phyogs
NG0505:2994: phyogs mtshams go 'byed nam mkha' ste //
NG0505:2995: dbyer med 'dres nas rtsi mi dgos //
NG0505:2996: so so'i phyogs dang kha dog dang *//
NG0505:2997: dbyibs dang sgra zin la rtag pa //
NG0505:2998: snod bcud phyi nang legs nyes bstan //
NG0505:2999: dkar po chu la dbyibs ni zlum //
NG0505:3000: ser po sa la gru bzhi ste //
NG0505:3001: dmar po gru gsum me'i rigs //
NG0505:3002: rlung ni ljang khu zla kham pa //
NG0505:3003: nam mkha' mthing gsal dbyibs dang bral //
NG0505:3005: chu sgra sa byed sa sgra rlung *//
NG0505:3006: rlung sgra mkha' la me yis tshig / me sgra chu la sa yis gnod //
NG0505:3007: grogs po de las bzlog pa ste //
NG0505:3008: gcig gis gcig smad sgra zin la //
NG0505:3009: gcig gis gcig bskyed grogs yin te //
NG0505:3010: cha snyoms zo la btang snyoms gnas //
NG0505:3011: de'i mtshan nyid bstan pa ni //
NG0505:3012: 'jig rten bstan bzhag rig pa'i gnas //
NG0505:3013: lo gcig zla ba bcu gnyis la //
NG0505:3014: dus kyi bye brag bstan pa ni //
NG0505:3015: dbyar gsum zla ba chu'i dus //
NG0505:3016: rtsi bcud thams cad skyed par byed //
NG0505:3017: ston gsum zla ba sa'i dus //
NG0505:3018: rtsi bcud thams cad skyed par byed //
NG0505:3019: dgun gsum zla ba me'i dus //
NG0505:3020: rtsi bcud thams cad skems par byed //
NG0505:3021: dpyid gsum zla ba rlung gi dus //
NG0505:3022: rtsi bcud thams cad stong par byed //
NG0505:3023: de bzhin nang gi sems can gyi //
NG0505:3024: lus dang longs spyod de yis shes //
NG0505:3025: de ltar 'byung ba ma snyoms na //
NG0505:3026: sgra yis rkyen pas nyes pa la //
NG0505:3027: grogs kyi yon tan rang la mnyam //
NG0505:3028: phyi rol pa dang nang dag gi / 'jig rten bstan chos rig pa dang *//
NG0505:3029: de yis brtag thabs kun shes 'gyur //
NG0505:3031: dang por chus skyed sa bstan pa'i //
NG0505:3032: lus skyed rdzogs par dar ba yin //
NG0505:3033: de nas me nyams rgas pa dang *//
NG0505:3034: tha ma rlung gis nad skyed nas //
NG0505:3036: de ni nang gi 'byung chen gyi //
NG0505:3037: bskal pa chags 'jig stongs gnas yin //
NG0505:3038: skabs su 'byung ba sgra zin gyis //
NG0505:3039: bde sdug mtho dman legs nyes kun //
NG0505:3040: legs par brtsis la bstan chos bya //
NG0505:3041: mkhas pa skyon med yon tan la //
NG0505:3042: bstan pa thob phyir bstan bcos zhes //
NG0505:3043: 'jig rten mkhyen pa rig pa'i gnas //
NG0505:3044: shes bya sna tshogs rig pa la //
NG0505:3045: chos dang chos min ngo bo gnyis //
NG0505:3046: shan 'byed dngul gyi me long la //
NG0505:3047: ma rig ma rig bskyed pa dang *//
NG0505:3048: phyin ci log gi shes rab kyis //
NG0505:3049: yang dag log par khrid pa rnams //
NG0505:3050: chos min 'khor ba'i bya ba yin //
NG0505:3051: shes rab shes rab bskyed nas su //
NG0505:3052: yang dag lam la 'jug pa rnams //
NG0505:3053: chos nyid don gyi bya ba yin //
NG0505:3054: mkhas pa 'di nyid shes par bya //
NG0505:3055: shes bya'i bud shing skam po la //
NG0505:3056: yang dag shes rab me 'bar bas //
NG0505:3057: nyon mongs bsreg pa'i ye shes kyis //
NG0505:3059: 'jug pa pha rol phyin mchog ldan //
NG0505:3060: sa bcu'i lam gnas mthar phyin pa'i //
NG0505:3061: kun don yon tan gsum thob bya'i //
NG0505:3063: pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa byang chub lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las /
NG0505:3064: shes bya'i chos thams cad gtan la dbab pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0505:3065: / gnas lugs bden pa dbyer med la //
NG0505:3066: stong pa'i rang bzhin ma 'gags pas //
NG0505:3067: snang ba sna tshogs ci shar yang *//
NG0505:3068: rang shar ma gtogs kun rdzob la //
NG0505:3069: gnang ba'i mtshan nyid ma nges pa //
NG0505:3070: stong pa nyid du rang grol la //
NG0505:3071: spros bral rig pa'i don dam la //
NG0505:3072: snang dang stong pa gnyis su bstan //

NG0505:3502: dbang bskur thams cad mkhyen pa ru //

NG0505:3536: stobs cher gyur pa'i gnyis pa la //

NG0505:3564: zhing khams mthong dang lung ston dang *//
NG0505:3565: rnam pa sna tshogs rtags rnams 'byung *//
NG0505:3566: byung yang mi rtag 'gyur ba yin //
NG0505:3567: sbyor lam dus su ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0505:3568: sgo ni brgya stong du ma mthong *//
NG0505:3569: snang ba rmi lam sgyu mar rtogs //
NG0505:3570: zag bcas zag med la sogs pa'i //
NG0505:3571: cha mthun mngon shes 'phra mo dang *//
NG0505:3572: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten ji snyed pa'i //
NG0505:3574: nyan thos rang rgyal ting 'dzin la //

NG0505:3576: chos rnams kun gyi don mthong bas //

NG0505:3581: bsgom lam dus na thob pa yin //

NG0505:3586: rtsal sbyong rgyu mthun rgyal rigs thob //
NG0505:3587: thams cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas spyan //
NG0505:3588: mthar phyin lam la rdzogs nas thob //

NG0505:3590: khams gsum nyon mongs spangs pa yi //

NG0505:3592: chos nyid don shes chos shes la //

NG0505:3594: rjes su shes pa mthong ba'i lam //
NG0505:3595: pha rol gzhan gyis sems shes pa //
NG0505:3596: sgrib pa med pa'i ye shes thugs //
NG0505:3597: sems can bsam pa shes pa yin //

NG0505:3599: zag bcas shes pa'i rtog pa rnams //
NG0505:3600: zag med mnyam nyid shes pa'o //
NG0505:3601: sdug bsngal shes par 'khor ba yi //
NG0505:3602: sdug bsngal rgyu mtshan shes pa'o //

NG0505:3604: nyon mongs rang bzhin shes pa'o //
NG0505:3607: chos la gang yang spangs su med //
NG0505:3608: mi mthun phyogs dang sdug bsngal bral //

NG0505:3612: sgrib pa zad par shes pa'o //

NG0505:3617: don gyi ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NG0505:3618: 'bras bu sku lnga ye shes lnga //

NG0505:3657: sems can skye shi yid rang bzhin //

NG0505:3678: rgyu yod 'bras bu med pa dang *//

NG0505:3682: rgyu yod 'bras bu med pa'i phyir //

NG0505:3695: de nyid las su mi 'dod na //
NG0505:3696: na tsha nyid kyang ma grub ste //
NG0505:3697: lus la las ni med pa'i don //
NG0505:3698: gal te nad ni grub pa na //
NG0505:3699: 'bras bu med pa'i dam bca' nyams //
NG0505:3700: mtshon gyi zug rngu byung bas gsal //

NG0505:3702: sdig byed mkhan po gang nas grub //

NG0505:3708: mkhan po ma grub khyod kyi skyon //

NG0505:3743: med la yod 'dzin log pa'i chos //

NG0505:3745: mi rtag sdug bsngal ya re che //

NG0505:3767: phyogs su ma lhung kun tu gsal //

NG0505:4242: dang mnyam pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs so ///

NG0505:4250: / e ma sangs rgyas bstan pa rin chen gyi //

NG0505:4252: byang chub lam gyi rgyud chen 'di //
NG0505:4253: stong gsum gzhan na ma mchis pa'i //
NG0505:4254: rgyal ba'i bka' lung bdag la gtad //
NG0505:4256: 'dzam gling gzhan du ma spel bar //
NG0505:4257: phyi rab lnga brgya'i tha ma la //

NG0505:4260: yi ger bkod nas gter du sbas //
NG0505:4261: o rgyan rigs 'dzin thugs kyi sras //

NG0505:4263: thub par srungs cig sa ma ya /
NG0505:4267: bdag 'dra rin chen gling pa la //
NG0505:4268: o rgyan pad+ma'i thugs rje yis //
NG0505:4269: bka' lung rje'i phyag nas byung *//
NG0505:4270: zab mo thugs kyi dgongs gter bton //
NG0505:4271: nyams len rgya gar yul du byas //
NG0505:4272: sgrub rtags o rgyan yul du bstan //
NG0505:4273: 'gro don bod kyi yul du byas //
NG0505:4274: dga' ldan gnas su dgongs pa rdzogs //
NG0505:4275: bde ba can du don gnyis rdzogs //
NG0505:4276: gter chos zab mo rgya mtsho nas //
NG0505:4277: khyad mchog byang chub lam rgyud @#//

NG0505:4280: lcag po 'brug la gdan drangs nas //
NG0505:4281: bla ma'i bka' bzhin shog ser nas //

NG0505:4284: 'di dus ngo mtshar can gyi rtags //

NG0505:4287: gter nas gdan drangs zhal bshus pa'i //
NG0505:4288: yi ge 'di nyid mthong thos dran //
NG0505:4289: yid la mos byed dpe mtshon nas //
NG0505:4290: mkha' mnyam 'gro kun ma lus pa //
